790
01:15:37,033 --> 01:15:38,743
The flavor is...

791
01:15:41,788 --> 01:15:44,122
This is really precious stuff.

792
01:15:44,123 --> 01:15:45,955
Have a drink.

793
01:15:45,956 --> 01:15:47,043
It's warming me up.

794
01:15:49,253 --> 01:15:50,421
Is there any more of the...

