805
01:16:30,378 --> 01:16:31,838
Thank you, Gwang-sim.

806
01:16:32,796 --> 01:16:34,048
I'll call back soon.

807
01:16:40,846 --> 01:16:42,056
Grandma.

808
01:16:43,723 --> 01:16:44,890
Grandma...

809
01:16:49,605 --> 01:16:51,356
